{"id":574173,"date":[{"year":1978,"month":12,"day":19}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"新长征","column":"","genre":"","count":"464","ytitle":"","mtitle":"常忆二首","ftitle":"","authors":["吕剑"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余以《常忆》为题得诗若干首。初意连续写来，勉作建国小史视之，然多未整理。兹先选出其中两首刊出，借以求正。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"}]}